'''抵制中國貨'''（{{lang-en|Boycott Chinese products}}），或稱'''抵制中國製造'''，是[[經濟|經濟]][[抵制|抵制]]的一種，目標為由[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]]所持有或及生產的商品。一般認為抵制中國貨的原因是領土爭端、[[2019冠狀病毒病|2019冠狀病毒病]]以及對中國獨裁專制的反對<ref>{{cite web | url = http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/lucknow/City-cleric-gives-call-to-boycott-Chinese-products/articleshow/44636071.cms | title = Lucknow cleric gives call to boycott Chinese products | author =  | date =  | accessdate = October 19, 2014 | publisher =  | language =  | archive-date = 2019-10-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191028223046/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/lucknow/City-cleric-gives-call-to-boycott-Chinese-products/articleshow/44636071.cms | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="sft-canada.org">{{cite web| url =http://www.sft-canada.org/campaigns/economic/boycott-made-in-china/| title =Boycott Made in China : SFT Canada – Students for a Free Tibet Canada| author =| date =| accessdate =October 19, 2014| publisher =| language =| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20141016013014/http://www.sft-canada.org/campaigns/economic/boycott-made-in-china/| archivedate =2014年10月16日| df =}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://opinion.inquirer.net/32863/the-call-to-boycott-chinese-products | title = The call to boycott Chinese products | author =  | date =  | accessdate = October 19, 2014 | publisher =  | language =  | archive-date = 2021-02-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210227083156/https://opinion.inquirer.net/32863/the-call-to-boycott-chinese-products | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[印度|印度]]、[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]以及中國的[[分離主義|分離主義]]組織曾經發起抵制[[中國貨|中國貨]]的運動。普遍認為完全抵制中國貨是困難的，因為該國產品在全世界廣泛銷售和使用，而且有很多外資企業在中國內地設立工廠或者委託中國內地的工廠來生產商品<ref>{{cite web|url = http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/chennai/Netizens-clamour-for-boycott-of-Made-in-China-products/articleshow/19888903.cms|title = Netizens clamour for boycott of ‘Made in China’ products|author = |date = |accessdate = October 20, 2014|publisher = |language = |archive-date = 2020-11-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201121151319/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/chennai/Netizens-clamour-for-boycott-of-Made-in-China-products/articleshow/19888903.cms|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 起因 ==
{{Rough translation}}
中國是全世界人口最多的大國，並且是面積第三大的國家，有很長的邊境線並與數個國家相鄰<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/ch.html | title = The World Factbook | author =  | date =  | accessdate = October 22, 2014 | publisher =  | language =  | archive-date = 2016-10-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161013030611/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/ch.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。歷史上，中國與其鄰國發生過許多次衝突<ref name="xiaobing">Xiaobing Li (2012). ''China at War: An Encyclopedia''. Publisher ABC-CLIO. ISBN 1598844156. Preface XV.</ref>。1949年，中华人民共和國成立。從後，中國領導人以經濟發展為第一優先<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.japantimes.co.jp/opinion/2008/11/11/commentary/china-japan-can-help-by-helping-themselves/#.VEbqR_msWvM | title = China, Japan can help by helping themselves | author =  | date =  | accessdate = October 22, 2014 | publisher =  | language =  | archive-date = 2019-12-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191201152850/https://www.japantimes.co.jp/opinion/2008/11/11/commentary/china-japan-can-help-by-helping-themselves/#.VEbqR_msWvM | dead-url = no }}</ref>。中國商家常常根據市場預期來調整產品的生產，<ref>Pula, Gabor& Santabárbara, Daniel (March 2011). [http://www.ecb.europa.eu/pub/pdf/scpwps/ecbwp1310.pdf Is China climbing up the quality ladder? Estimating cross country differences in product quality using Eurostat's COMEXT trade database] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ecb.europa.eu/pub/pdf/scpwps/ecbwp1310.pdf |date=20191112144155 }}. WORKING PAPER SERIES.</ref>，而海外消費者選擇的是其低廉的價格。

[[价廉物美|价廉物美]]是一個間接原因。許多印度公司無法找到足夠的所需原材料以製造消費者所需的產品，反而用一些中国公司模仿[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]、[[凱悅酒店|凱悅酒店]]以及[[星巴克|星巴克]]這類國際知名公司所制作的產品<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.theguardian.com/world/2012/oct/17/china-fake-apple-shops-romney | title = China's fake Apple shops point to impatience for the newest products | author =  | date =  | accessdate = October 24, 2014 | publisher = the Guardian | language =  | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112033250/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2012/oct/17/china-fake-apple-shops-romney | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.forbes.com/sites/michaelzakkour/2014/04/30/copycat-china-still-a-problem-for-brands-chinas-future-just-ask-apple-hyatt-starbucks/ | title = Copycat China Still A Problem For Brands & China's Future: Just Ask Apple, Hyatt & Starbucks | author =  | date =  | accessdate = October 24, 2014 | publisher = Forbes | language =  | archive-date = 2020-11-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201125065315/https://www.forbes.com/sites/michaelzakkour/2014/04/30/copycat-china-still-a-problem-for-brands-chinas-future-just-ask-apple-hyatt-starbucks/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，或是既模仿其知名商標又模仿整個商店<ref>{{cite web | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/money/industries/technology/2011-07-31-China-counterfeiting-fake-Western-goods-stores_n.htm | title = China takes knock-offs to a new level, copying entire stores - USATODAY.com | author =  | date =  | accessdate = October 28, 2014 | publisher = USATODAY.COM | language =  | archive-date = 2020-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201111194043/https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/money/industries/technology/2011-07-31-China-counterfeiting-fake-Western-goods-stores_n.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 抵制活動 ==
=== {{IND}} ===
由於2014年中印邊境衝突的關係，[[印度|印度]]和[[西藏流亡政府|西藏流亡政府]]聯合發起抵制中國貨的運動<ref>{{cite web | url = http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Indo-Tibetan-meet-proposes-boycott-of-Chinese-goods/articleshow/22914680.cms | title = Indo | author =  | date =  | accessdate = October 20, 2014 | publisher =  | language =  | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308050135/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Indo-Tibetan-meet-proposes-boycott-of-Chinese-goods/articleshow/22914680.cms | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://zeenews.india.com/news/uttar-pradesh/boycott-chinese-products-says-prominent-cleric-in-eid-sermon_1480643.html | title = Boycott Chinese products, says prominent cleric in Eid sermon | author =  | date =  | accessdate = October 20, 2014 | publisher = Zee News | language =  | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225013328/https://zeenews.india.com/news/uttar-pradesh/boycott-chinese-products-says-prominent-cleric-in-eid-sermon_1480643.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。印度[[国民志愿服务团|国民志愿服务团]]領袖{{link-en|莫漢·巴格瓦特|Mohan Bhagwat}}宣佈：「我們談論關於自立和抗衡中國。新政府似乎是抗衡它了。但是如果我們不抵制購買中國貨，政府何以從中汲取力量呢？」<ref>{{cite web | url = http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/mohan-bhagwat-says-ban-chinese-goods-rss-chief-dd-telecast/1/394013.html | title = Boycott Chinese goods, says RSS chief Mohan Bhagwat in DD telecast : India, News | author =  | date =  | accessdate = October 20, 2014 | publisher =  | language =  | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304113542/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/mohan-bhagwat-says-ban-chinese-goods-rss-chief-dd-telecast/1/394013.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。一些印度商店因爲兩國之間的衝突而開始抵制中國貨<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.savetibet.org/shops-in-india-join-chinese-goods-boycott-campaign/ | title = Shops in India join Chinese goods boycott campaign | author =  | date =  | accessdate = October 20, 2014 | publisher =  | language =  | archive-date = 2019-12-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191201080843/https://savetibet.org/shops-in-india-join-chinese-goods-boycott-campaign/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

在非实体商品方面，2020年5月，受[[2020年中印邊境衝突|中印邊境衝突]]影響，印度开发团队“初创公司”推出“移除中国应用程式（Remove China Apps）”的应用。此應用於6月3日因其违反谷歌的部分政策而下架<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.guancha.cn/internation/2020_06_03_552815.shtml |title=印度团队开发“移除中国App”，被谷歌下架 |accessdate=2020-06-18 |archive-date=2020-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200618154053/https://www.guancha.cn/internation/2020_06_03_552815.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。6月29日，印度宣布禁用59款中國大陸手機應用程式，其中包括TikTok、微信、UC瀏覽器<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://udn.com/news/story/7333/4733042|title=微信印度服務喊停 商家叫苦|work=經濟日報|author=蔡敏姿|date=2020-07-27|accessdate=2020-07-27|archive-date=2020-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906225717/https://udn.com/news/story/7333/4733042|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== {{PHL}} ===
在菲律賓，有不同的團體發起全國性的抵制「中國製造」運動<ref>{{cite web | url = https://ph.news.yahoo.com/filipino-vietnamese-americans-call-boycott-made-china-products-091003080.html | title = Filipino, Vietnamese Americans call for boycott of 'Made in China' products | author = News Desk in Washington/Philippine Daily Inquirer | date =  | accessdate = October 19, 2014 | publisher = Yahoo News Philippines | language =  | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141019183920/https://ph.news.yahoo.com/filipino-vietnamese-americans-call-boycott-made-china-products-091003080.html | archivedate = 2014年10月19日 }}</ref>。由於2012年[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]與中國因[[黃岩島主權問題|黃岩島主權問題]]而發生衝突，[[阿爾拜省|阿爾拜省]]省長{{link-en|喬伊·薩爾斯達|Joey Salceda}}支持菲律賓人抵制中國貨<ref>{{cite web| url =http://news.asiaone.com/News/Latest+News/Asia/Story/A1Story20110613-283760.html| title =Philippine governor calls for boycott of 'Made in China' products| author =| date =| accessdate =October 19, 2014| publisher =| language =| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20141021160008/http://news.asiaone.com/News/Latest%2BNews/Asia/Story/A1Story20110613-283760.html| archivedate =2014年10月21日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://globalnation.inquirer.net/37179/albay-gov-renews-call-for-boycott-of-china-products/ | title = Albay gov renews call for boycott of China  products | author =  | date =  | accessdate = October 20, 2014 | publisher =  | language =  | archive-date = 2020-07-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200710191648/https://globalnation.inquirer.net/37179/albay-gov-renews-call-for-boycott-of-china-products | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== {{VNM}}===
由於[[南中國海|南中國海]]主權爭議，越南與中國的關係緊張，尤其是[[海洋石油981|海洋石油981]]鑽井平臺的設立觸發了越南抵制中國貨的運動<ref>{{cite web | url = http://learningenglish.voanews.com/content/vietnamese-boycott-chinese-products/1972975.html | title = Vietnamese Boycott Chinese Products | author =  | date =  | accessdate = October 19, 2014 | publisher = VOA | language =  | archive-date = 2016-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305051007/http://learningenglish.voanews.com/content/vietnamese-boycott-chinese-products/1972975.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在[[2014年越南排華暴動|2014年越南排華暴動]]中，{{cn|越南人通過抵制中國貨、使用越南貨來表達他們在南中國海爭端上的愛國主義精神。}}

=== {{KOR}} ===
2017年因[[韓國部署薩德反導彈系統事件|韓國部署薩德反導彈系統事件]]引起争端，中国掀起抵制韩货运动，[[韩国|韩国]]社会反弹，出现抵制中國貨呼声。

=== {{TIB}}流亡殖民者 ===
[[十四世達賴喇嘛|十四世達賴喇嘛]]的長兄[[土登晉美諾布|土登晉美諾布]]發起抵制中國貨的運動，以尋求[[西藏獨立運動|西藏獨立]]<ref name="sft-canada.org"/><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.savetibet.org/shops-in-india-join-chinese-goods-boycott-campaign/ | title = Shops in India join Chinese goods boycott campaign | author =  | date =  | accessdate = October 19, 2014 | publisher =  | language =  | archive-date = 2019-12-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191201080843/https://savetibet.org/shops-in-india-join-chinese-goods-boycott-campaign/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.phayul.com/news/article.aspx?id=3612&t=1 | title = Tibetans campaign for boycott of Chinese goods during Kalachakra prayers | author =  | date =  | accessdate = October 19, 2014 | publisher =  | language =  | archive-date = 2014-10-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141016135255/http://www.phayul.com/news/article.aspx?id=3612&t=1 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他說：「我確信，抵制中國貨的運動能夠獲得全世界支持自由的慈愛人士的支持，且最終能夠成功迫使中國關心自己人民的人權並承認[[圖博|圖博]]獨立。……我號召所有圖博人和朋友們加入我們純潔、神聖的解放祖國的鬥爭中來。」<ref>[[Barry_Sautman|Barry Sautman]], June Teufel Dreyer (2006). Contemporary Tibet: Politics, Development, and Society in a Disputed Region. Publisher M.E. Sharpe. ISBN	0765613549. Page 72.</ref>

